	<li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="comment-5971">

		
		<div class="comment-author vcard">
			<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/e8155c5ab5e53b03dfdadaf57cc81199?s=48&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />			<cite class="fn"><a href='http://noblepig.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Cathy @ Noble Pig</a></cite> <span class="says">says:</span>	 	</div><!-- end .comment-author -->

		<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata">
			<a href="http://www.savorysimple.net/grapefruit-curd-ice-cream/#comment-5971">August 31, 2012 at 10:21 am</a>
					</div><!-- end .comment-meta -->

		<div class="comment-content">
			
			<p>I just used lemon curd to make ice cream, but store bought. Never thought of other types of curd. This sounds amazing and the color is beautiful!!</p>
		</div><!-- end .comment-content -->

		<div class="reply">
			<a class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-5971' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-5971", "5971", "respond", "6127")'>Reply</a>		</div>

		</li>
			</ol>
